{% doc %}
  @prompt
    
    
     
    
    ### 🎯 Objective:
    
    Create a professional, modern **Featured Collection** section for Shopify (OS 2.0 compatible) with full customization settings in schema. Section must support both grid and slider layout with condition-based rendering.
    
    ---
    
    ## 🔹 Section Requirements:
    
    ### 1️⃣ Header / Rich Text Area
    
    * Section heading (richtext)
    * Subheading (optional richtext)
    * Text alignment option (left / center / right)
    * Heading size option (small / medium / large / custom px)
    * Margin bottom setting
    
    ---
    
    ### 2️⃣ Collection Settings
    
    * Collection picker (dynamic collection select)
    * Option to choose:
    
      * Number of products to show (range: 2–20)
      * Products per row (desktop)
      * Products per row (tablet)
      * Products per row (mobile)
    
    ---
    
    ### 3️⃣ Layout Settings
    
    Add toggle:
    
    * Layout type:
    
      * Grid
      * Slider (enable if products > selected limit)
    
    Slider Conditions:
    
    * Enable slider after X products
    * Autoplay (true/false)
    * Autoplay speed (ms)
    * Navigation arrows toggle
    * Dots toggle
    * Infinite loop toggle
    
    Condition:
    If total products > products_per_row → enable slider automatically (if enabled in setting).
    
    ---
    
    ### 4️⃣ Product Card Design Settings
    
    Each product card must include:
    
    * Product image
    * Product title
    * Product rating (Shopify rating metafield compatible)
    * Product price (compare at price support)
    * Quick View button
    * Add to Cart button (optional toggle)
    
    ---
    
    ### 5️⃣ Hover Effects
    
    Settings:
    
    * Enable hover scale effect (true/false)
    * Scale intensity (1.02 – 1.1)
    * Image zoom on hover toggle
    * Show secondary image on hover toggle
    * Quick View button show:
    
      * Always
      * On Hover
      * Disabled
    
    ---
    
    ### 6️⃣ Product Content Layout Settings
    
    Options:
    
    * Title position:
    
      * Below image
      * Overlay bottom
      * Overlay center
    * Content alignment:
    
      * Left
      * Center
      * Right
    * Show rating toggle
    * Show price toggle
    
    ---
    
    ### 7️⃣ Card Styling Settings
    
    Provide full customization:
    
    * Card background color
    * Card border toggle
    * Border width (px)
    * Border color
    * Border radius (px)
    * Card padding (px)
    * Box shadow toggle
    * Shadow intensity
    
    ---
    
    ### 8️⃣ Image Settings
    
    * Image ratio:
    
      * Square
      * Portrait
      * Landscape
      * Adapt to image
    * Image border radius
    * Image fit:
    
      * Cover
      * Contain
    * Image position (center / top / bottom)
    
    ---
    
    ### 9️⃣ Section Styling
    
    * Section background color
    * Section padding top/bottom
    * Container width:
    
      * Full width
      * Boxed
    * Max width setting
    
    ---
    
    ### 🔟 Advanced Conditions
    
    * If collection is empty → show placeholder products
    * If rating metafield not available → hide rating automatically
    * If product has no compare_at_price → hide compare price
    * If only 1 product → disable slider automatically
    * Fully responsive layout
    
    ---
    
    ## 🧩 Technical Requirements:
    
    * Shopify OS 2.0 section (JSON schema)
    * Liquid based
    * No external heavy libraries (use lightweight slider like Swiper or CSS scroll snap)
    * Performance optimized
    * Lazy loading images
    * Use Shopify image_url filter properly
    * Use dynamic metafield rating support
    * Clean and modular CSS (BEM preferred)
    * Accessibility support (aria labels)
    
    ---
    
    ## 🎨 Design Reference:
    
    Modern military-style bold product card layout
    Dark theme compatible
    Smooth hover animation
    Minimal and premium feel
    
    ---
    
    ## 🔥 Expected Output:
    
    * Complete `.liquid` section file
    * Proper `{% schema %}` settings
    * CSS included inside section
    * JS included (if slider enabled)
    * Fully dynamic & reusable
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% liquid
  assign collection = block.settings.collection
  assign products_to_show = block.settings.products_to_show
  assign layout_type = block.settings.layout_type
  assign enable_slider = block.settings.enable_slider
  assign products_per_row_desktop = block.settings.products_per_row_desktop
  assign products_per_row_tablet = block.settings.products_per_row_tablet
  assign products_per_row_mobile = block.settings.products_per_row_mobile
  
  if collection == blank
    assign products = all_products | limit: products_to_show
  else
    assign products = collection.products | limit: products_to_show
  endif
  
  assign total_products = products.size
  assign should_enable_slider = false
  
  if enable_slider and total_products > products_per_row_desktop
    assign should_enable_slider = true
  endif
%}

{% style %}
  .ai-featured-collection-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.section_bg_color }};
    padding-top: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    {% if block.settings.container_width == 'boxed' %}
      max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    {% else %}
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0 20px;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: {{ block.settings.text_alignment }};
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.header_margin_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    {% if block.settings.heading_size == 'small' %}
      font-size: 24px;
    {% elsif block.settings.heading_size == 'medium' %}
      font-size: 32px;
    {% elsif block.settings.heading_size == 'large' %}
      font-size: 48px;
    {% else %}
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_custom_size }}px;
    {% endif %}
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subheading_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat({{ products_per_row_desktop }}, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap }}px;
    {% if should_enable_slider == false %}
      margin: 0;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__slider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__slider-track-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap }}px;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__slider-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 0 0 calc((100% - ({{ products_per_row_desktop }} - 1) * {{ block.settings.grid_gap }}px) / {{ products_per_row_desktop }});
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    background: {{ block.settings.nav_bg_color }};
    border: none;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    z-index: 10;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__nav-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background: {{ block.settings.nav_hover_bg_color }};
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__nav--prev-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    left: 10px;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__nav--next-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    right: 10px;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    fill: {{ block.settings.nav_icon_color }};
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__dots-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__dot-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: {{ block.settings.dot_color }};
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-featured-collection__dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    background: {{ block.settings.dot_active_color }};
  }

  .ai-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    background: {{ block.settings.card_bg_color }};
    {% if block.settings.card_border %}
      border: {{ block.settings.card_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.card_border_color }};
    {% endif %}
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding }}px;
    {% if block.settings.card_shadow %}
      box-shadow: 0 {{ block.settings.shadow_intensity }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_intensity | times: 2 }}px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    {% endif %}
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  {% if block.settings.enable_hover_scale %}
    .ai-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
  {% endif %}

  .ai-product-card__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.image_border_radius }}px;
    {% if block.settings.image_ratio == 'square' %}
      aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    {% elsif block.settings.image_ratio == 'portrait' %}
      aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    {% elsif block.settings.image_ratio == 'landscape' %}
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-product-card__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: {{ block.settings.image_fit }};
    object-position: {{ block.settings.image_position }};
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  {% if block.settings.image_zoom_hover %}
    .ai-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-product-card__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }
  {% endif %}

  .ai-product-card__image-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: {{ block.settings.image_fit }};
    object-position: {{ block.settings.image_position }};
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  {% if block.settings.show_secondary_image %}
    .ai-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-product-card__image-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  {% endif %}

  .ai-product-card__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    {% if block.settings.title_position == 'overlay-bottom' or block.settings.title_position == 'overlay-center' %}
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding }}px;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.7), transparent);
      color: #ffffff;
      {% if block.settings.title_position == 'overlay-bottom' %}
        bottom: 0;
      {% else %}
        top: 50%;
        transform: translateY(-50%);
      {% endif %}
    {% else %}
      margin-top: 12px;
    {% endif %}
    text-align: {{ block.settings.content_alignment }};
  }

  .ai-product-card__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    {% if block.settings.title_position == 'below-image' %}
      color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    {% else %}
      color: #ffffff;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-product-card__rating-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    {% if block.settings.content_alignment == 'center' %}
      justify-content: center;
    {% elsif block.settings.content_alignment == 'right' %}
      justify-content: flex-end;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-product-card__rating-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    fill: #ffa500;
  }

  .ai-product-card__price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    {% if block.settings.title_position == 'below-image' %}
      color: {{ block.settings.price_color }};
    {% else %}
      color: #ffffff;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-product-card__compare-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-decoration: line-through;
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-right: 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .ai-product-card__quick-view-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    background: {{ block.settings.quick_view_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.quick_view_text_color }};
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
    {% if block.settings.quick_view_visibility == 'on-hover' %}
      opacity: 0;
    {% elsif block.settings.quick_view_visibility == 'disabled' %}
      display: none;
    {% endif %}
  }

  {% if block.settings.quick_view_visibility == 'on-hover' %}
    .ai-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-product-card__quick-view-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  {% endif %}

  .ai-product-card__quick-view-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background: {{ block.settings.quick_view_hover_bg_color }};
  }

  .ai-product-card__add-to-cart-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    background: {{ block.settings.add_to_cart_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.add_to_cart_text_color }};
    border: none;
    padding: 12px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-product-card__add-to-cart-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background: {{ block.settings.add_to_cart_hover_bg_color }};
  }

  .ai-product-card__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background: #f4f4f4;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.image_border_radius }}px;
  }

  .ai-product-card__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    max-width: 200px;
    max-height: 200px;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-featured-collection__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ products_per_row_tablet }}, 1fr);
    }

    .ai-featured-collection__slider-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex: 0 0 calc((100% - ({{ products_per_row_tablet }} - 1) * {{ block.settings.grid_gap }}px) / {{ products_per_row_tablet }});
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-featured-collection__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ products_per_row_mobile }}, 1fr);
    }

    .ai-featured-collection__slider-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex: 0 0 calc((100% - ({{ products_per_row_mobile }} - 1) * {{ block.settings.grid_gap }}px) / {{ products_per_row_mobile }});
    }

    .ai-featured-collection__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      {% if block.settings.heading_size == 'small' %}
        font-size: 20px;
      {% elsif block.settings.heading_size == 'medium' %}
        font-size: 24px;
      {% elsif block.settings.heading_size == 'large' %}
        font-size: 32px;
      {% else %}
        font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_custom_size | times: 0.7 }}px;
      {% endif %}
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<featured-collection-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-featured-collection-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-featured-collection__container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.heading != blank or block.settings.subheading != blank %}
      <div class="ai-featured-collection__header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
          <h2 class="ai-featured-collection__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.subheading != blank %}
          <div class="ai-featured-collection__subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.subheading }}</div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if should_enable_slider %}
      <div class="ai-featured-collection__slider-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-slider>
        {% if block.settings.show_nav_arrows %}
          <button class="ai-featured-collection__nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-featured-collection__nav--prev-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-prev aria-label="Previous">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M15 18l-6-6 6-6"/></svg>
          </button>
          <button class="ai-featured-collection__nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-featured-collection__nav--next-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-next aria-label="Next">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>
          </button>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ai-featured-collection__slider-track-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-track>
          {% for product in products %}
            <div class="ai-featured-collection__slider-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <div class="ai-product-card__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {% if product.featured_image %}
                    <img
                      src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                      alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                      class="ai-product-card__image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                      loading="lazy"
                      width="800"
                      height="800"
                    >
                    {% if block.settings.show_secondary_image and product.images[1] %}
                      <img
                        src="{{ product.images[1] | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                        alt="{{ product.images[1].alt | escape }}"
                        class="ai-product-card__image-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                        loading="lazy"
                        width="800"
                        height="800"
                      >
                    {% endif %}
                  {% else %}
                    <div class="ai-product-card__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                    </div>
                  {% endif %}

                  {% if block.settings.quick_view_visibility != 'disabled' %}
                    <button class="ai-product-card__quick-view-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-label="Quick view {{ product.title }}">
                      Quick View
                    </button>
                  {% endif %}
                </div>

                <div class="ai-product-card__content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <h3 class="ai-product-card__title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    <a href="{{ product.url }}">{{ product.title }}</a>
                  </h3>

                  {% if block.settings.show_rating and product.metafields.reviews.rating.value %}
                    <div class="ai-product-card__rating-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {% assign rating = product.metafields.reviews.rating.value %}
                      {% for i in (1..5) %}
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                          {% if i <= rating %}
                            <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
                          {% else %}
                            <path d="M22 9.24l-7.19-.62L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21 12 17.27 18.18 21l-1.63-7.03L22 9.24zM12 15.4l-3.76 2.27 1-4.28-3.32-2.88 4.38-.38L12 6.1l1.71 4.04 4.38.38-3.32 2.88 1 4.28L12 15.4z"/>
                          {% endif %}
                        </svg>
                      {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                  {% endif %}

                  {% if block.settings.show_price %}
                    <div class="ai-product-card__price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {% if product.compare_at_price > product.price %}
                        <span class="ai-product-card__compare-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ product.compare_at_price | money }}</span>
                      {% endif %}
                      <span>{{ product.price | money }}</span>
                    </div>
                  {% endif %}

                  {% if block.settings.show_add_to_cart %}
                    <button class="ai-product-card__add-to-cart-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-label="Add {{ product.title }} to cart">
                      Add to Cart
                    </button>
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          {% else %}
            {% for i in (1..products_to_show) %}
              <div class="ai-featured-collection__slider-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <div class="ai-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <div class="ai-product-card__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    <div class="ai-product-card__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="ai-product-card__content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    <h3 class="ai-product-card__title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Product Title</h3>
                    {% if block.settings.show_price %}
                      <div class="ai-product-card__price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">$0.00</div>
                    {% endif %}
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            {% endfor %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>

        {% if block.settings.show_dots %}
          <div class="ai-featured-collection__dots-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-dots></div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    {% else %}
      <div class="ai-featured-collection__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% for product in products %}
          <div class="ai-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-product-card__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% if product.featured_image %}
                <img
                  src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                  alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                  class="ai-product-card__image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  loading="lazy"
                  width="800"
                  height="800"
                >
                {% if block.settings.show_secondary_image and product.images[1] %}
                  <img
                    src="{{ product.images[1] | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                    alt="{{ product.images[1].alt | escape }}"
                    class="ai-product-card__image-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                    loading="lazy"
                    width="800"
                    height="800"
                  >
                {% endif %}
              {% else %}
                <div class="ai-product-card__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                </div>
              {% endif %}

              {% if block.settings.quick_view_visibility != 'disabled' %}
                <button class="ai-product-card__quick-view-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-label="Quick view {{ product.title }}">
                  Quick View
                </button>
              {% endif %}
            </div>

            <div class="ai-product-card__content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <h3 class="ai-product-card__title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <a href="{{ product.url }}">{{ product.title }}</a>
              </h3>

              {% if block.settings.show_rating and product.metafields.reviews.rating.value %}
                <div class="ai-product-card__rating-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {% assign rating = product.metafields.reviews.rating.value %}
                  {% for i in (1..5) %}
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      {% if i <= rating %}
                        <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
                      {% else %}
                        <path d="M22 9.24l-7.19-.62L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21 12 17.27 18.18 21l-1.63-7.03L22 9.24zM12 15.4l-3.76 2.27 1-4.28-3.32-2.88 4.38-.38L12 6.1l1.71 4.04 4.38.38-3.32 2.88 1 4.28L12 15.4z"/>
                      {% endif %}
                    </svg>
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
              {% endif %}

              {% if block.settings.show_price %}
                <div class="ai-product-card__price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {% if product.compare_at_price > product.price %}
                    <span class="ai-product-card__compare-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ product.compare_at_price | money }}</span>
                  {% endif %}
                  <span>{{ product.price | money }}</span>
                </div>
              {% endif %}

              {% if block.settings.show_add_to_cart %}
                <button class="ai-product-card__add-to-cart-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-label="Add {{ product.title }} to cart">
                  Add to Cart
                </button>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
          </div>
        {% else %}
          {% for i in (1..products_to_show) %}
            <div class="ai-product-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-product-card__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <div class="ai-product-card__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ai-product-card__content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <h3 class="ai-product-card__title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Product Title</h3>
                {% if block.settings.show_price %}
                  <div class="ai-product-card__price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">$0.00</div>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</featured-collection-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

{% if should_enable_slider %}
  <script>
    (function() {
      class FeaturedCollection{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
        constructor() {
          super();
          this.slider = this.querySelector('[data-slider]');
          this.track = this.querySelector('[data-track]');
          this.prevBtn = this.querySelector('[data-prev]');
          this.nextBtn = this.querySelector('[data-next]');
          this.dotsContainer = this.querySelector('[data-dots]');
          this.currentIndex = 0;
          this.autoplayInterval = null;
          this.itemsPerView = {{ products_per_row_desktop }};
          this.totalItems = {{ total_products }};
          this.autoplay = {{ block.settings.autoplay }};
          this.autoplaySpeed = {{ block.settings.autoplay_speed }};
          this.infiniteLoop = {{ block.settings.infinite_loop }};
        }

        connectedCallback() {
          this.setupEventListeners();
          this.createDots();
          if (this.autoplay) {
            this.startAutoplay();
          }
          this.updateSlider();
        }

        setupEventListeners() {
          if (this.prevBtn) {
            this.prevBtn.addEventListener('click', () => this.prev());
          }
          if (this.nextBtn) {
            this.nextBtn.addEventListener('click', () => this.next());
          }

          window.addEventListener('resize', () => this.handleResize());
        }

        handleResize() {
          if (window.innerWidth <= 749) {
            this.itemsPerView = {{ products_per_row_mobile }};
          } else if (window.innerWidth <= 989) {
            this.itemsPerView = {{ products_per_row_tablet }};
          } else {
            this.itemsPerView = {{ products_per_row_desktop }};
          }
          this.updateSlider();
        }

        createDots() {
          if (!this.dotsContainer) return;
          
          const totalSlides = Math.ceil(this.totalItems / this.itemsPerView);
          this.dotsContainer.innerHTML = '';
          
          for (let i = 0; i < totalSlides; i++) {
            const dot = document.createElement('button');
            dot.className = 'ai-featured-collection__dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}';
            dot.setAttribute('aria-label', 'Go to slide ' + (i + 1));
            if (i === 0) dot.classList.add('active');
            dot.addEventListener('click', () => this.goToSlide(i));
            this.dotsContainer.appendChild(dot);
          }
        }

        updateSlider() {
          const gap = {{ block.settings.grid_gap }};
          const itemWidth = (this.track.offsetWidth - (gap * (this.itemsPerView - 1))) / this.itemsPerView;
          const offset = -(this.currentIndex * (itemWidth + gap));
          this.track.style.transform = 'translateX(' + offset + 'px)';
          this.updateDots();
        }

        updateDots() {
          if (!this.dotsContainer) return;
          const dots = this.dotsContainer.querySelectorAll('.ai-featured-collection__dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
          dots.forEach((dot, index) => {
            if (index === this.currentIndex) {
              dot.classList.add('active');
            } else {
              dot.classList.remove('active');
            }
          });
        }

        next() {
          const maxIndex = Math.ceil(this.totalItems / this.itemsPerView) - 1;
          if (this.currentIndex < maxIndex) {
            this.currentIndex++;
          } else if (this.infiniteLoop) {
            this.currentIndex = 0;
          }
          this.updateSlider();
          this.resetAutoplay();
        }

        prev() {
          const maxIndex = Math.ceil(this.totalItems / this.itemsPerView) - 1;
          if (this.currentIndex > 0) {
            this.currentIndex--;
          } else if (this.infiniteLoop) {
            this.currentIndex = maxIndex;
          }
          this.updateSlider();
          this.resetAutoplay();
        }

        goToSlide(index) {
          this.currentIndex = index;
          this.updateSlider();
          this.resetAutoplay();
        }

        startAutoplay() {
          this.autoplayInterval = setInterval(() => {
            this.next();
          }, this.autoplaySpeed);
        }

        resetAutoplay() {
          if (this.autoplay) {
            clearInterval(this.autoplayInterval);
            this.startAutoplay();
          }
        }

        disconnectedCallback() {
          if (this.autoplayInterval) {
            clearInterval(this.autoplayInterval);
          }
        }
      }

      customElements.define('featured-collection-{{ ai_gen_id }}', FeaturedCollection{{ ai_gen_id }});
    })();
  </script>
{% endif %}

